sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor C as Client
  participant A as actix handler<br/>(PUT /{path})
  participant N as NIP-98 verify<br/>(auth::nip98)
  participant W as WacEvaluator<br/>(wac.rs)
  participant L as LdpService<br/>(ldp.rs)
  participant S as Storage backend<br/>(trait Storage)
  participant M as Server-managed<br/>triples

  C->>A: PUT /alice/notes/foo.ttl<br/>Authorization: Nostr <b64>
  A->>N: verify(header, method, url, body_hash)
  alt auth fails
    N-->>A: PodError::Unauthorized
    A-->>C: 401 Unauthorized
  else auth ok
    N-->>A: Nip98Verified { pubkey, webid }
    A->>W: evaluate_access(path, mode=Write, webid)
    W->>S: head(path.acl)  /* ACL lookup */
    S-->>W: AclDocument | NotFound
    alt denied
      W-->>A: AccessMode::None
      A-->>C: 403 Forbidden
    else allowed
      W-->>A: AccessMode::Write
      A->>L: put(path, body, content_type)
      L->>S: put(path, bytes, mime)
      S-->>L: ResourceMeta { etag, size, mtime }
      L->>M: add dc:modified, stat:size
      M-->>L: extended meta
      L-->>A: ok(meta)
      A-->>C: 201 Created<br/>ETag, Link: rel=type
    end
  end

  Note over A,S: Any storage IO error → PodError → 5xx<br/>Any RDF parse error → 400 Bad Request
